1. Molim te, *zatvori* prozor jer je hladno napolju. (Please, *close* the window because it's cold outside.)
2. Policija je morala *zatvoriti* cestu zbog prometne nesreće. (The police had to *close* the road due to a traffic accident.)
3. Nisam mogao spavati jer sam zaboravio *zatvoriti* vrata. (I couldn't sleep because I forgot to *close* the door.)
4. Ovo je poslednja prilika da *zatvorite* ugovor sa nama. (This is the last opportunity to *close* a deal with us.)
5. Kada sam ušao u sobu, mama je odmah *zatvorila* knjigu. (When I entered the room, my mom immediately *closed* the book.)
6. Da li si siguran da si *zatvorio* slavinu? (Are you sure you *closed* the tap?)
7. *Zatvorila* je oči i pustila suzu kada joj je saopštila tužnu vest. (She *closed* her eyes and shed a tear when she was told the sad news.)
8. Bilo je neophodno *zatvoriti* kompaniju zbog finansijskih problema. (It was necessary to *close* the company due to financial problems.)
9. Dok su ostali gosti otišli kući, on je *zatvorio* kafić. (While the other guests went home, he *closed* the café.)
10. Moram da *zatvorim* ovaj projekat pre nego što odem na odmor. (I need to *close* this project before I go on vacation.)